Title: Abu Dhabi Beige Interchangeable Back Strap
Body (HTML):
Our Abu Dhabi Beige is your go-to bra for all of your outfit needs. Wear it strapless or hook shoulder straps on for multi-way wear. You know you'll be covered for any occasion with this back strap!

Hidden closures located on the sides of the back straps leave a seamless look across your back as well as more balanced support and more adjustment options to provide a better fit.

Multi-loop button hole elastic options along the top inside of the back strap allow you to wear multiple shoulder straps at the same time or to move them around to fit your trickiest wardrobe needs. 

Silicone strip across the inside back strap gives a non slip support while going strapless. Best of all, you can mix and match any back strap to our cups.

Sizing: 26-30 (approx 13 1/2in. long) accommodates band sizes 26,28,30. 30-34 (approx 15 1/2in. long) accommodates band sizes 30,32,34. 34-38 (approx 17 1/2in. long) accommodates band sizes 34,36,38.

  • Made of Nylon Spandex
  • Hand wash and lay flat to dry
  • Each item is sold separately, shoulder straps are not included

Body (HTML):
Jamie Harten is a wife and mother from Glenn Dale, Maryland. Her personal style is inspired by color, pattern and texture.  She loves the mix and match versatility of The Bra Lab. Jamie was diagnosed with type 1 diabetes as a young child. She manages the disease with modern technology, but hopes for a cure one day. When you buy a Jamie Lee back strap, we will make a donation to the Juvenile Diabetes Research Foundation. 
The Juvenile Diabetes Research Foundation funds research, advocates new treatments and provides support for millions of people impacted by type 1 diabetes. You can support the cause for a cure! For more information, go to https://www.jdrf.org

 

Hidden closures located on the sides of the back straps leave a seamless look across the back as well as more balanced support and more adjustment options to provide a better fit.

Multi-loop button hole elastic options along the top inside of the back strap allow you to wear multiple shoulder straps at the same time or to move them around to fit your trickiest wardrobe needs. 

Silicone strip across the inside back strap gives a non slip support while going strapless. Best of all, you can mix and match any back strap to our cups.

Sizing: 26-30 (approx 13 1/2in. long) accommodates band sizes 26,28,30. 30-34 (approx 15 1/2in. long) accommodates band sizes 30,32,34. 34-38 (approx 15 1/2in. long) accommodates band sizes 34,36,38.

Each item is sold separately, shoulder straps are not included. You must purchase a Bra Lab cup to wear with our back straps. 

Not sure which bra to get? For general questions send us an email shop@thebralab.com or a pic of your outfit to our stylist gigi@thebralab.com

Material: Nylon/Spandex

Care: Hand wash, lay flat to dry.

Patented Design
